HEADWORD: Vierkleur
<hw>Vier"kleur`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[D., fr.
<ets>vier</ets> four + <ets>kleur</ets> color, F.
<ets>couleur</ets>.]</ety> <def>The four-colored flag of the South
